<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <title>邀请好友</title>
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width,initial-scale=1,minimum-scale=1,maximum-scale=1,user-scalable=no" />
    <meta name="apple-mobile-web-app-capable" content="yes">
    <meta name="apple-mobile-web-app-status-bar-style" content="black">
    <meta name="format-detection" content="telephone=no" />
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="../css/sm.min.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="../css/invite_friend.css?version=2002">
    <script type='text/javascript' src='../js/zepto.min.js'></script>
    <script type='text/javascript' src='../js/sm.min.js'></script>
    <script type='text/javascript' src='../js/base.js?version=2002'></script>
</head>
<body>
<div class="page">

    <div class="content">
        <div class="top_box">还未邀请到好友开店哦</div>

        <div class="mid_box">
            <div class="mid_pic"><img src="../img/financeShoppingGoldBars.png" alt=""></div>
            <div class="mid_text">把成为店长的种种福利带给您的朋友<br/>
                TA成为店长时都会带给你30元现金奖励<br/>请一定要让他们输入您的专属邀请码哦
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="invite_code">
            <div class="code_big">使用微信分享功能将该页面发给您的好友</div>
            <div class="code_text">或使用您的专属邀请码</div>
            <div class="code_box" id="inviteCode">3456786</div>
        </div>
        <div class="down_box">
            <div class="down_text">即可邀请好友开店</div>
            <!--<div class="down_btn" id="invteBtn">邀请好友开店</div>-->
        </div>

        <div class="foot_box">
            <div class="question">
                <div class="que_item">
                    <div class="que_title one">什么是邀请码</div>
                    <div class="answer"><p>邀请码是您的专属店铺序号。</p>
                        <p>好友通过您的邀请码开店，会给您带来邀请奖励并可以获取TA开店后所产生销售额的额外奖励。</p>
                        <p>一定记得要分享给您的好友哦~</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="que_item">
                    <div class="que_title two">成功邀请好友您将获得</div>
                    <div class="answer">
                        <p>每成功邀请一位好友开店，可获得30元现金奖励</p>
                        <p class="se">TA的店铺产生的销售现金收益，全民集市将额外给您商品售价10%-50%的销售奖励</p>
                        <p class="plus">店长奖励策略会根据时间不同而调整，最终解释权归杭州四体科技所有
                        </p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

    </div>
</div>
</body>
<script type="text/javascript" src="http://res.wx.qq.com/open/js/jweixin-1.0.0.js"></script>
<script type='text/javascript' src='../js/invite_friend.js?version=2002'></script>
</html>